!.env.example

# Logs & Debugging
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
**/*.trace
/coverage/
*.lcov

# Editor & System
.idea/
.vscode/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
